Name: Canister Filter Aquarium External Aqua Pump Fish Water Tank Sponge Pond 1000L/H
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Create a healthy and prosperous habitat for your marine life with our ergonomically built External Filter. Nurturing sea animals has always been a complicated task, one that requires attention and equipment that is precisely calibrated to support the flimsy life cycle of aqua dwellers. Usually, these filters are bulky, oversized, and not at all economical. To tackle these practical issues, we have devised out a model that is compact, portable, and reliable. Built with marvelous engineering to provide an impeccable freshwater supply to your aquarium.

Featuring an advanced filtration system with a multi-layered structure of biological, mechanical, and chemical filters. No matter what the waste, no matter what the contamination, this filter can deal with it all. A flawless combination that works simultaneously round the clock to ensure a pure, constant, and steady stream of supply to the tank. Use its adjustable valve to control the flow of water, simple adjustments for a controlled environment. You can also shut the flow of water using the provided shut off tap, all of the convenience right at your fingertips.

Marine life is a delicacy to handle which is why our product comes equipped with a state-of-the-art UV light sterilization system to decimate the accumulation of algae, harmful microbes, and damaging micro-organisms. Targets and eliminates the impurities with ultra-precision the result of which is a source of water supply that helps your sea life to survive, brings joy, and most of important of it all, it can simply make them happy!

Made of high-quality PVC material. Built tough with a casing made of durable ABS for added stability and strength. Greatly compatible, use it for saltwater or freshwater aquariums. The entire structure is sealed with tight grip to prevent any leakage of water. Consumes less power for hassle-free use. Very easy and simple to use, it can be easily set up with no tools. Hassle-free usage with inlet and outlet connectors.     

A freshness it provides, a clean stream it enables, a hygiene it indulges. Start filtering! Order one now.

Key Features:

  • 1000L/H 14W      Efficient external filter
  • Ultra-low power consumption
  • Multi-level biological, mechanical,and chemical filtering system
  • Water flow shut off tap
  • Adjustable water flow
  • 4-Level filtration
  • Compact and durablecasing
  • Quick connect style hoses and fitting
  • Leakage proof tight cap lock
  • Water flow control switch
  • Easy installing inlet andoutlet connector
  • Suits both freshwater and saltwater aquariums
  • Simpleset up, no tools needed
SPECIFICIATION
  • Material: ABSplastic 
  • Filter power: 14W
  • Water flow rate: 1000L/H
  • Voltage: 100V/220V/240V
  • Frequency: 50Hz/60Hz
  • Hose length: 1.5m
